# About
Ephp, so easy!!!

# Character
(1) easy & fast
(2) don't use namespace
(3) Nginx or Apache rewrite the url, not php

# Code rule
(1) variable name use lowercase and underline
(2) model class
1. file name "usermodel.php" class name "usermodel"
2. only model class have CONST

# Env
Linux Nginx PHP Redis

# Request
(1) php extension phpredis

# Nginx.conf
if (!-d $request_filename) {
    rewrite ^/([a-z]+)/([a-z]+)/?(.*)$ /index.php?ctrl=$1&act=$2$3 last;
    break;
}

# Vist example
localhost/ctrl/act?query_string
	
